title: Saxophonist Lakecia Benjamin performs Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Lakecia Benjamin performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded March 11, 2025.

Songs:
Phoenix Reimagined 01:06
Let Go 04:23
